<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11311</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"我得去市政府一趟。"罗西想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她跑向朋友们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19648</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗨，朋友们，我刚想起一件事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我必须……嗯……写一篇读书报告。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33250</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一会儿见！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37572</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔看着罗西跑远了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37573</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40425</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真奇怪。”他心想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40426</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43679</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“老师没让写读书报告啊。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43680</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47110</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西到了市政府。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52163</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探正在跟布洛姆市长的秘书谈话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52164</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55427</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“......在那之后，”秘书说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55428</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布洛姆市长就从市政府走掉了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59060</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64826</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不知道他为什么要偷走那笔钱。”史密斯侦探说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64827</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72233</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许布洛姆市长想请一个新秘书。”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72234</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74778</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她盯着秘书。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74779</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得你在撒谎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80607</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布洛姆市长才不是小偷。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80608</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83514</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>秘书皱起眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83515</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我没撒谎。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这件事，我跟你一样吃惊。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94729</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯哼。”史密斯侦探看着罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94730</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“吵架是没有用的，火箭女孩儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102171</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西叹了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103907</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说得对。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103908</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你知道布洛姆市长去哪儿了吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他留下什么线索了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110708</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113555</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有。”秘书说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113556</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116189</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，在把钱拿走之前，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116190</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119250</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他接到了一个可疑的电话。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁打来的？”史密斯侦探问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129441</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>秘书查看了一下市长的电话记录。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129442</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133994</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“电话是从美罗城大学的实验室打来的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133995</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的，火箭女孩儿。”史密斯侦探说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144426</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要去......火箭女孩儿？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144427</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150799</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西来到美罗城大学的实验室。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150800</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155725</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个巨大的实验箱立在墙边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155726</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>电线和线圈把实验箱和一个大电脑连在一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168095</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个黑发男人坐在电脑前，戴着厚厚的眼镜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168096</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173855</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一直在等你，火箭女孩儿。”那个男人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173856</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你一定在找布洛姆市长吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182298</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是谁？”罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185230</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男人微笑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185231</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187790</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是迪托教授。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187791</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191910</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西听到身后有脚步声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191911</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195365</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她转过身去，看到另外一个男人，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199128</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>长得跟迪托教授一模一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199129</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203930</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也是迪托教授。”那个男人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203931</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209462</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>又一个男人走进实验室。“我也是。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209463</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213158</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西惊讶得直眨眼睛 。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213159</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216436</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>更多的男人出现在他身后。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216437</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219708</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每一个都长得一模一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219709</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223447</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们都是迪托教授！”罗西想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223448</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226964</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男人们向罗西靠近。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226965</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231180</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西向后后退了几步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236631</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，他们把罗西推进一个实验箱里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236632</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239660</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>实验箱的门关上了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239661</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西大声喊叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>电流嗡嗡接通了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245033</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>灯光闪烁，火花四溅。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接着，实验室安静了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256513</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西被拉出了实验箱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256514</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260724</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看到另外一个实验箱里，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260725</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264179</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有人从里面走出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264180</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267726</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西吓得倒吸一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267727</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273723</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>另一个火箭女孩儿出现了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>